verses.verse: God be mercifull vnto vs, blesse vs, & shewe the light off his countenauce apon vs.
Sela. That we maye knowe yi waye vpo earth, yi sauynge health amonge all Heithen.
Let the people prayse the (o God) yee let all people prayse the.
O let the people reioyse and be glad, that thou iudgest the folke rightuously, and gouernest the nacions vpo earth.
Let the people prayse the (o God) let all people prayse the.
God (euen oure owne God) geue vs his blessinge, that the earth maye bringe forth hir increase
God blesse vs, and let all the endes of ye worlde feare him.
